item.title: Risk Warning
item.description: Important information Past performance is not a guide to future performance, nor a reliable indicator of future results or performance. The value of investments, and the income or capital entitlement which may derive from them, if any, may go down as well as up and is not guaranteed; therefore, investors may not get back the amount originally invested. Unless the performance of an investment meets or exceeds the rate of inflation, the real value of that investment will reduce.
